sentences.sentence: CORONAVIRUS  Norwegian scientist claims coronavirus was made in Chinese lab by · Jun 8th, 2020 2:07 pm 14 A Norwegian scientist has claimed the novel coronavirus that has infected more than 6.7 million people worldwide was manufactured in a Chinese lab .
new study published by virologist Birger Sørensen and British professor Angus Dalgleish has found that the coronavirus' spike protein contains sequences that appear to be artificial.
Their research also revealed the virus' lack of mutation since its discovery, which indicates it was already fully adapted to humans.
Sørensen said COVID-19 has properties that differ greatly from SARS, a viral respiratory illness caused by a coronavirus.
These properties have never been detected in nature.
Sørensen also noted that Chinese scientists were the first to release the sequences his team claimed to have been unnatural.
Sir Richard Dearlove, former head of the British intelligence agency MI6, said he also believes the virus originated in a lab.
"I think this started as an accident.This raises the question of whether China will assume responsibility and whether China should pay compensation," Dearlove said.

"It's a risky business if you make a mistake.Look at the stories of the attempts by the leadership to lock down any debate about the origins of the pandemic and the way that people have been arrested or silenced."
